1. In the PAS tile, select **File Storage**.
1. For **Max Valid Packages per App**, Pivotal recommends leaving the default value of `5`. However, you may want to lower the value if you have strict storage requirements and want to use less disk space. 
1. For **Max Staged Droplets per App**, Pivotal recommends leaving the default value of `5`. However, you may want to lower the value if you have strict storage requirements and want to use less disk space.  
1. For **Configure your Cloud Controller's filesystem**, see [Select File Storage Location](#cc-filesystem). 
